    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Learn more how customers reviews work on Amazon

    Customers say

    Customers find these headphones decent for the price, with good sound quality and functionality working well on all PCs. However, they receive mixed feedback about comfort, with some finding them comfortable while others say they hurt after a short time. Moreover, durability is a concern as they break within a couple of weeks, and the fit is inconsistent with some saying it's good while others find them too tight on the ears. Additionally, the noise isolation receives mixed reviews, with some praising the excellent noise isolation while others report obnoxious interference.

      5.0 out of 5 stars Impressive Wired Headphones for Audio Enthusiasts
      Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
      Size: USB-CStyle: Headphones with MicVerified Purchase
      I recently purchased a pair of wired headphones, and I must say, they have completely elevated my audio experience. Here's a detailed review:

      Sound Quality:
      The standout feature of these headphones is undeniably the exceptional sound quality. The clarity, depth, and balance across the entire spectrum are remarkable. Whether I'm listening to music, watching movies, or gaming, the headphones deliver a rich and immersive audio experience. The bass is deep without being overpowering, and the highs and mids are crisp and detailed.

      Comfort:
      Comfort is crucial for extended listening sessions, and these headphones excel in that department. The ear cushions are plush and provide a snug fit without causing discomfort. The adjustable headband ensures a customized fit for various head sizes. I can wear them for hours without any signs of fatigue or discomfort.

      Build Quality:
      The build quality of these headphones is impressive. The materials used feel durable and sturdy, giving the headphones a premium look and feel. The adjustable headband and swiveling ear cups add to the overall flexibility and durability of the design. The detachable cable is a practical feature that adds to the longevity of the headphones.

      Noise Isolation:
      The headphones offer excellent noise isolation, effectively blocking out external sounds and allowing me to enjoy my audio without distractions. This is particularly beneficial when using them in noisy environments or during travel.

      Cable and Connectivity:
      The wired connection provides a reliable and uninterrupted audio experience. The included cable is of high quality and has a sufficient length, giving me flexibility in my movements while connected to various devices. The universal compatibility ensures that I can use these headphones with a wide range of audio sources.

      Overall, these wired headphones have exceeded my expectations. They strike an impressive balance between outstanding audio quality, comfort, and durability. If you're an audio enthusiast looking for a reliable pair of wired headphones, I highly recommend considering this option. They deliver a premium listening experience that is well worth the investment.

    About this Item

    • High-quality stereo sound - powerful 40mm drivers with Deep bass and a wide dynamic range deliver an exceptional listening experience
    • Best-in-class comfort - the headphones' padded headband is designed to fit heads of all ages and the foam ear pads provide hours of comfortable use
    • 6 foot USB cord - built to be strong enough for heavy use
    • Single-sided monitoring enabled - the ear cups swivel to enable others to listen in
    • Safe listening limit - the maximum output is set to 94Db to prevent hearing loss
    • Connectivity Technology: Wired

    Product Description

    The Kensington USB Hi-Fi headphones provides high-quality stereo sound a microphone designed to support voice clarity and best-in-class comfort Features The headphones provide a max output of 94dB for safe listening making them perfect for students business professionals and recreational gamers Compatible with Windows Mac and chrome OS for a simple plug-and-play experience
